column5: Great, private guest room with Cable TV/DVD, closet, private bathroom, use of common areas and washer/dryer, and WiFi. Southwest Austin / Safe Neighborhood. Less than 10 miles from Downtown, 7 miles from Zilker, 4 miles from Barton Creek Green Belt, and 20 mins from Airport. I do have an extra air mattress if two guests.
column8: Cozy/Private Room in Nice Home close to Downtown
